title: WritePresentValueNullWithPriority (Method)
text:
METHOD WritePresentValueNullWithPriority : CmpBACnet.IEC_BACNET_STATUS
Set the Present_Value to NULL with the given priority taking client side restrictions into account (access, priorization, range checks).
In contrast to
SetPropertyInstance
and
|PresentValue.Set|
all access, priorization and range checks are executed by this call and on return
the occurred BACnet error code will be returned.

rows.Name: priority
rows.Comment: The priority to use when writing to Present_Value.
